This work is has some usage restrictions. The goal is to prevent commercial redistribution and modification while granting end users as much freedom as possible.

You are free:

▪ To copy & distribute the content in it's present form non commercially (on a file sharing site, Bittorrent, Usenet, with friends etc)
▪ To produce works from the content. (Such as musical compositions, sound design etc).
▪ To modify, transform and build upon the content for any non-commercial purpose (your free soft synth for instance).
▪ To copy & distribute your modified content non commercially.

You may not:

▪ Sell the content, in any form, without prior permission.
▪ Develop commercial products with the content without prior permission (this includes synthesisers, samples libraries).


For more information please contact modularsamples@gmail.com.